sentences: Caylee Anna Hammack (born March 17, 1994) is an American country music singer and songwriter.
She is signed to Capitol Records Nashville and released her debut album If It Wasn’t For You on August 14, 2020.
She moved at the end of 2013 with about $1000 of savings, a high school diploma, her clothes in trash bags, and playing Kacey Musgraves debut album for the seven-hour drive.
